n: Dairy-Free Peanut Butter and Banana Smoothie
des: "This is a quick dairy-free smoothie. It is great as a quick breakfast or a cool afternoon snack."
ins: Blend coconut milk, banana, peanut butter, and honey in a blender until smooth, about 1 minute. Add ice and blend again until the ice is crushed, 2 to 3 minutes.
